Fionna (Flac IntO Normal/Native Audio). 

Fionna is audio converter for people who have a personal music library in open-source lossless audio codec and needs to have some music in MP3 for:
    portable player
    usb flash stick to use in car radio with usb
    etc.

Fionna is minimalistic and very easy-to-use. It lets you to copy a lot of flac tracks directly to mp3 with same filenames to given disk or path WITH NO any MP3 in your collection!
